ActFarm Credit Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of JACK C. CHRISTIE of Miramichi, New Brunswick, as a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, effective November 27, 2003, in the place of Robert M. Colpitts, whose term will expire.
